  "texts": [
    "For round 1, we constructed training sets to train the generative models of CuSOD and MDH.",
    "We collected 6,003 CuSOD and 4,765 MDH sequences from UniProt (Supplementary Table 2) with the Pfam domains for each protein family.",
    "CuSOD sequences had only a single Sod_Cu domain, whereas MDH sequences had an Ldh_1_N domain followed by an Ldh_1_C domain and no other Pfam domains.",
    "Nontypical domain architectures occurred in 6.3% and 1.7% of sequences in CuSOD and MDH, respectively.",
    "Sequences were truncated around the annotated domains to remove possible signal peptides, transmembrane domains and extraneous unannotated domains."
  ],
